Algorithm

Frae Wikipedia
Lowp tae: navigation, rake

In mathematics an computer science, an algorithm (i/ˈælɡərɪðəm/ AL-gə-ri-dhəm) is a step-bi-step procedure for calculations. Algorithms are uised for calculation, data processin, an automatit reasonin.
